high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter with the microwave on the right.
Pick up the fork behind the green sponge on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the fork inside the left side of the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn left to face the drawers to the right of the stove.
Open the left drawer next to the stove, put the rinsed fork inside and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed fork in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn right to walk to the microwave.
Pick up the fork next to the microwave on the counter.
Turn left to walk to the sink.
Rinse the fork in the sink.
Turn left to face the drawer directly below the avocado on the counter.
Put the fork away in the drawer below the avocado.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a fork to put it in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around, walk forward to the sink, then turn right and walk to the microwave.
Pick up the fork on the counter to the left of the microwave.
Turn around, walk forward slightly, then turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the fork in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn left towards the stove top.
Put the fork in the top drawer just to the right of the stove top, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned fork in a drawer.
